Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is good for the freshman in the university live on campus dorm during thr first year of college. When they live in campus in the first year, they can make more friends with others. And they can talk a lot with the people in the dorm. They can know more about the university.